  <header>
    <h1>Building a Reproducible Mining Pipeline for the Scandinavian Runic-text Database (SRD) via Runor (RAÄ) and the SRD REST API</h1>

    <details class="meta">
      <summary>Métadonnées</summary>

      <div class="meta-body">
        <p>Arvid Narimani (2025)</p>
        <p>ORCID : <a href="https://orcid.org/0009-0001-1001-4065">https://orcid.org/0009-0001-1001-4065</a></p>
        <p>Dernière version : <a href="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.18037067">https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.18037067</a></p>
        <p>Version citée : v1 — <a href="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.18037067">https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.18037067</a></p>
